{"tid":672213,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【假結衣】大陸網紅龍夢柔拍日劇 負評不絕被嫌口大😯","createTime":"2018-05-20T19:32:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T12:39:31.000Z","uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":118,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"4f66a344eea1aa8550d7c77845a30c0ec9894a90","tid":672213,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T19:32:12.000Z","msg":"法國真係幾大<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7870acc59978e57519e8e2f261139f6f13867871","tid":672213,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T19:32:26.000Z","msg":"大陸網紅龍夢柔以「中國新垣結衣」姿態進軍日本，繼拍攝東急stay廣告之後，有指佢計劃出碟做歌手，仲處女接拍日劇，演出中村杏擔正深夜劇《愛情重跑》，在第七集中登場。"},{"pid":"34d1843c362785716b415ad2c02545295748b2bc","tid":672213,"uid":44730,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T19:32:50.000Z","msg":"龍夢柔於2014年參加《來吧！灰姑娘》獲得冠軍，其後走紅網絡以栗子之名發展。今次呢位冒牌結衣BB在劇中角色都叫栗子，同飾演主角南沙也加嘅中村杏都有對手戲。可惜，劇集出街後引來唔少日本網民狂踩，指佢同正版完全唔似樣，既彈佢口大，又話「中國新垣結衣」呢個稱號十分過譽，與結衣BB完全係比下去咁話。"},{"pid":"d83fa6fa3c5fe8f9f916e5866d7ad0aa2af6eac4","tid":672213,"uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":25,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T19:33:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/davNk1v2WnI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdavNk1v2WnI&d=roPBnFQFRfcH9bYbT%2BtJnZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=7a553ed2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/davNk1v2WnI</a><br />\n<br />\n拍日劇 負評不絕被嫌口大"},{"pid":"bd859ac844d038534e197003df3cee30a10ae61b","tid":672213,"uid":44730,"like":61,"dislike":3,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T19:34:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180519/large/1526740443_dca6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple